Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平  來幫下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  今天的鍛煉結束了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正準備去沖個澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒幹一場了試試如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開店準備已經做好了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子要想繼承家業的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也差不多該來幫下忙學會工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說要繼承了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家想幹的事可多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色色的事情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…那種事也有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平  說過叫你來幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  你拿著做生意的工具搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  像有了兩個孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}昨晚7時左右  在涉谷區居住的45歲資本家在公路上被人謀殺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}類似的事件與去年相比呈現出多發態勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種事真多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊者只盯著有錢人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我們家沒啥關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平  如果你被捲進這樣的事件中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦的  反正被盯上的也是富人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了  如果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「船到橋頭自然直」嗎…哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老爸你遇上了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然是「船到橋頭自然直」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就像有了兩個孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又遲到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平  不准你騎摩托上學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些日子你的老師才跟媽媽提過意見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只把它騎到學校的附近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不能算是回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這孩子到底像誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像孩子他媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  你拿著做生意的工具在幹嘛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是  我所見到的我爸媽的…最後一面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  這兩個月來…一直都在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…準備去一心先生那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在突然叫我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…船到橋頭自然直吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了襲擊資產家的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎樣？  哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我阿爾弗在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等無禮的粗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…但是現在絕不可放開韁繩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是上等貨色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒問你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該這樣吧…老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙搞什麼…不是赤手空拳麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你吃我一棍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老管家  那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  要來硬的了  請回到車內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快把那小子處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…我不再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我先處理你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受不了了  一群惡棍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老管家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老管家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下死翹翹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…大意了吧臭老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能保護好大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿爾弗已經…沒有任何繼續活著的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就讓我來超度你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爛攤子還是要好好收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對黑澤爾林克家動手的這份罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好親身體驗體驗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那起到了墊子的作用才得救了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有塊墊子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…太好了  你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…午安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說「晚安」好像有些太早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…你什麼也不記得了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得馬車開到了山路上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我叫什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的  我叫夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特·黑澤爾林克  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說那種謊話呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小林哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特…黑澤爾…林克？名字聽上去簡直就像個公主一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我就是個公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說那種謊話呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太習慣這種的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是習慣亂摸昏睡中的女孩子的胸啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是偶爾…對  只是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  那麼我就相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  你是我的救命恩人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這不是記得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摸了我的胸  我騙了你  算抵消吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的「抵消」我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  男孩子果然更喜歡胸大的女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個…要因人…而異的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩托車壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…比想像中的要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了哦  和不認識的男生在一起會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那確實挺可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  那個馬車…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:18.76,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(282,251)}來電14個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:18.76,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(312,301)}您有電話留言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了  不趕緊回去把行李搬出去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓我有馬一心等待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我女兒佳苗的兒子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  我是被有馬一心叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種人有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背後背的那個  是太刀吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫警察吧  這違反了刀槍法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實站好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽人家說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小傢伙是我很重要的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄭重地款待他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一心大人的客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  一心先生  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能喊我外公麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺太突然了點…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「老爺子」怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸和老媽…不是死於事故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到仇人的話  怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報完以後又怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就換做你  成為別人的報仇目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那無止境的仇恨與悲傷的鎖鏈纏繞下活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佳苗和那個男人希望你度過的人生麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你對自己女兒的死一點悲傷都沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我有你在  我只剩下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…您穿的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要繼續這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會嚇到我們的來賓的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  問得晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼變成那副狼狽樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過救了個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  就這樣子亮相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了好事才弄髒的  有什麼好隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撐著我們有馬集團的各位董事以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位來賓  讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是  有馬哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的孩子  也是有馬財團總裁繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  繼承人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你們也被他那蓬頭垢面的樣子嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因為  他來這裡的路上救了一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你救了誰來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做「夏洛特·黑澤爾林克」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  黑澤爾林克家的公主殿下嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是功不可沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑澤爾林克公國？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是公主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…能讓大家興奮起來我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  不論對於他來說還是對於大家來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副樣子  確實有失禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能等我們修整一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期間  請大家自便暢談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  總裁繼承人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了報仇才來當你的養子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你找就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當上繼承人自然有人會不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了讓他們知道所以才讓你來和我演了一出雙簧戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白麼？  佳苗曾經是正式繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式…繼承人？  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人不可能馬上就露出馬腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你要培養自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有不是因為剛才的雙簧戲才親近你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要和這樣的人友好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平君  果然長得很像令尊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有馬集團屬下的專務椴村  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多的大人們圍堵一個年輕人可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵·侯森卿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侯森卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否賞臉讓我負責引領一心大人的孩子的任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是梵·侯森卿的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失態的一群人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都拼了命地要通過你  來和一心先生套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒作自我介紹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特·梵·侯森  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我介紹我的女兒們給你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  這個哥哥就是那個成為爺爺的孩子的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能亂說「爺爺」的吧？  真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見  她還不識禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我叫瑪利亞·梵·侯森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有馬哲平…請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得你有些矜持呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  希爾維呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不知道走哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  哲平君  今天嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦一心先生到場  氣氛就不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真強的統率力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身上  也能感覺到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多習慣這裡了吧  暫時先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平先生  有空的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…完全摸不著頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光保持儀態就耗盡精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…  你從一開始就對我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕…真的假的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來還像別的什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…的確除了女僕以外的什麼都不像……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的女僕啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平先生  您要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像現在這樣覺得摸不著頭腦的時候  運動運動身體是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想和西洋劍系的交一下手試試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小賊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真般配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「般配」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個哥哥  和姐姐一樣強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫「哥哥」還早了點呢  瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省下了不少功夫呢  哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過劍的交鋒  我相信你們兩個已經互相認識了吧  哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是希爾維婭·梵·侯森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚妻？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平的爸爸  總是提著一根棒狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底他是幹什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擀麵條的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  Princess Lover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園和再會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh  Japanese  Food啊  真不錯


